Package SmUtilities

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ABCSortPairs
    This class provides a sorting mechanism for pairs of numbers, one of which is the value to sort on and the other is an id.
    BuildAPKtable
    The BuildAPKtable class pulls information from the Cosmos headers and data arrays of the processed records and builds a CSV table for output.
    CommentFormatter
    Handles the updates to the Cosmos comment section as new processing steps are added.
    ConfigReader
    This class provides a collection to hold the configuration file parameters.
    CSVFileWriter
    The CSVFileWriter class creates a new csv file using the data and the headerline if the file with the given filename doesn't exist.
    FileRemovalCheck  
    FilterCornerReader
    This class provides a collection to hold the station filter corners.
    PrismLogger
    This class is a singleton instance of the prism logger.
    PrismXMLReader
    This class is a customized XML parser for the PRISM Strong Motion project.
    ProcessStepsRecorder2
    This class records the V2 processing steps so they can be included in the comments section of the product files.
    RecordIDValidator
    Validates the format of the record id before its use in building directory names and recording in the apktable
    SmDebugLogger
    This class is a singleton instance of the prism debug logger.
    SmTimeFormatter
    This class provides the current date and time in GMT time, according to the Gregorian calendar.
    TextFileReader
    This class is used to read from a text file and return the contents as an array of strings (text).
    TextFileWriter
    This class is used to write an array of text out to a file
